snippet.title: Of Mice and Moggies - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Of Mice and Moggies is a smart puzzle game, where you play a hungry cat that tries to catch cute animals.
Out now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1409180/Of_Mice_and_Moggies
